wrlinux-overc
===============

This layer provides the Wind River Linux specific OverC configuration
elements.  It will leverage the 'overc' distribution as defined by the
meta-overc layer, and add necessary Wind River Linux settings.

Dependencies
------------
This layer depends on OpenEmbedded Core, wr-template, wrlinux, overc, and
wrlinux-overc-cfg layers.


Maintenance
-----------
This layer is maintained by Wind River Systems, Inc.
Contact <support@windriver.com> or your support representative for more
information on submitting changes.


Building the wrlinux-overc layer
==================================

This layer should be added to the bblayers.conf file. To enable the software
provided by this layer, enable the distribution in the local.conf file. 

The OverC functionality can be enable by setting:

 DISTRO = "wrlinux-overc"


